Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪 片尾曲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那么要放片尾曲了哟
